    h2 Projects
    .row
      .span5
        img(src="img/projects.jpg")
        p Chloi is a believer in open source, we have created and maintained several projects in both the mobile-web and server-side application stack.
        p We are always looking for ways to give back to the community, whether is be training, community engagement, speaking or open source contributions.
        p Check out our <a href="http://github.com/chloi" target="_blank">github profile</a> for more information on our projects. Or drop us a line if you think we would be a good fit for your project, conference, or company.
      .span6.offset1
        .row
          .span2
            img(src="img/phonegap_logo.png", width="100%")
          .span4
            h4
              a(href="http://phonegap.com") PhoneGap
            p PhoneGap, a cross platform HTML5 mobile application stack. Leveraging open web standards and simplifying development by reducing code complexity and domain specific knowledge, while providing a native user experience. 
        .row
          .span2
            span.xui-logo XUI
          .span4
            h4
              a(href="http://xuijs.com") XUI
            p XUI was designed to be a light weight DOM and Event library for Mobile Application development. 
        .row
          .span4.offset2
            h4
              a(href="https://github.com/sintaxi/node-dbox") dbox
            p Dbox is a NodeJS SDK for the official Dropbox API. It abstracts the irrelevant detail of speaking to a REST API while exposing the bits that are important, such as status code and body.

